\c 10
\s Ukuru hwaModhekai
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo Ahasuwerusi wakaisa mutero panyika nepazviwi zvegungwa.
\v 2 Zvino basa rese resimba rake nedudziro yeukuru hwaModhekai, mambo hwaakamukurisa nahwo, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku reMakoronike emadzimambo eMedhiya nePerisiya?
\v 3 Nokuti Modhekai muJudha wakava wechipiri pana mambo Ahasuwerusi; ari mukuru pakati peVaJudha, uye achigamuchirwa nechaunga chehama, achitsvakira vanhu vake zvakanaka, uye achitaura rugare kumbeu yake yese.
